018-02-27T03:19:47.000Z","msg":"中国咁強大，返去係好事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:20:16.000Z","msg":"咪係，要不是中央照顧佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee8d7ed958df33e95965610403cb6af1355243a3","tid":573920,"uid":78429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:26:02.000Z","msg":"53歲就3個孫<br />\n呢啲唔係蝗蟲係乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62db54f9c2ca551c8c1a2dd0272b245a0c38c948","tid":573920,"uid":65074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:35:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>張敏在上訴時時承認自己犯了錯，但是她以人道主義和同情為由希望法官網開一面。她說自己已經將生活重心放在撫養3名年幼的外孫上。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中國人真係好興咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n犯法之後博鬼佬同情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n消費其他人嘅善良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a65a75579eb99285ed8de306ae3fdec5fda664","tid":573920,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:38:08.000Z","msg":"沒收財產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45775a187eb7b24b0cb34cb463ae09840d72d53","tid":573920,"uid":140588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:38:45.000Z","msg":"加拿大好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，陸續有來。"},{"pid":"ffc3489a31e57704accc7ab7fa1e362bbdd24edf","tid":573920,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0703d1da181971e148c5d0cb4c49c8bc3a9989cb","tid":573920,"uid":22422,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T02:32